# GitHub Actions (workflows and composite actions)

- **Lint:** Run `actionlint` on workflow and action files before finishing.
- **Project command:** `bun run lint:workflows` (uses system actionlint or `nix run nixpkgs#actionlint`).
- **Full check:** `bun run check` (includes actionlint). Use `check:with-links` to add lychee.
- **Workflow testing:** Prefer `bun run check:ci` (act) for local testing over pushing to CI.
- **Pins:** All actions are SHA-pinned. Auto-pr pins live only in `auto-pr.yml`; update `knirski/auto-pr@SHA` there when upgrading (use SHA from knirski/auto-pr main).